{
  "title": "Exotic Moroccan Coconut Tagine",
  "description": "A funky and crumbly Moroccan dish featuring meringue nests and coconut cream crack, served in a traditional molcajete vessel, jain friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Moroccan",
